WEBVTT

00:00:28.219 --> 00:00:30.161
Welcome to the blog.

00:00:30.181 --> 00:00:31.882
I am your host, Craig Winn,

00:00:31.981 --> 00:00:33.642
and this handsome fellow over here,

00:00:33.701 --> 00:00:34.762
he is the co-host.

00:00:35.283 --> 00:00:37.363
This is the indomitable Wookie.

00:00:38.223 --> 00:00:40.005
We're here to continue our story on the

00:00:40.284 --> 00:00:41.325
last word picture.

00:00:41.344 --> 00:00:44.847
We're reviewing what is said in the eighty

00:00:44.906 --> 00:00:45.807
ninth Mizmowr.

00:00:45.826 --> 00:00:49.529
And to set the scene for what is

00:00:49.588 --> 00:00:50.588
transpiring here,

00:00:50.628 --> 00:00:54.651
this is really the fulcrum.

00:00:55.753 --> 00:00:56.834
of human existence.

00:00:57.215 --> 00:00:59.776
I would go so far as to say

00:00:59.816 --> 00:01:03.337
that about the circumstances surrounding

00:01:03.496 --> 00:01:04.057
this song.

00:01:05.156 --> 00:01:07.918
You see, all the way from the beginning,

00:01:08.278 --> 00:01:10.438
all the way back to the garden,

00:01:10.498 --> 00:01:12.739
six thousand years ago,

00:01:13.140 --> 00:01:14.281
Yahowah was first born.

00:01:16.825 --> 00:01:18.646
Someone he just called the man,

00:01:18.825 --> 00:01:21.927
the first individual that Yahowah conceived

00:01:22.587 --> 00:01:26.989
in his image, giving him both a nephesh,

00:01:27.028 --> 00:01:28.390
which is consciousness,

00:01:28.829 --> 00:01:32.831
which all animals have, and uniquely,

00:01:33.152 --> 00:01:35.311
a Neshamah, a conscience,

00:01:35.893 --> 00:01:38.834
the ability to intelligently relate to

00:01:38.894 --> 00:01:39.054
