00:01:40.478 --> 00:01:43.200
we started an episode that was quite the

00:01:43.240 --> 00:01:44.781
experiment between God and man.

00:01:45.662 --> 00:01:46.162
He wondered,

00:01:46.462 --> 00:01:51.105
