00:02:06.468 --> 00:02:09.430
And so God created a microcosm of the

00:02:09.550 --> 00:02:11.150
earth in Eden,

00:02:12.350 --> 00:02:15.413
a place that was particularly conducive

00:02:15.832 --> 00:02:21.034
and uniquely beneficial to sustain life.

00:02:21.656 --> 00:02:23.396
And he placed his firstborn,

00:02:24.637 --> 00:02:27.699
this man called the man, Ha-Adam,

00:02:28.658 --> 00:02:29.379
in that place.

00:02:30.205 --> 00:02:32.326
And they began an interesting

00:02:32.366 --> 00:02:33.086
relationship,

00:02:34.048 --> 00:02:38.472
just that it didn't materialize as God had

00:02:38.512 --> 00:02:40.693
