00:02:40.752 --> 00:02:40.873
Now,

00:02:40.894 --> 00:02:42.534
I'm sure you haven't heard that unless

00:02:42.555 --> 00:02:44.156
you've listened to these programs that

00:02:45.016 --> 00:02:48.118
Adam was a bit of a flop.

00:02:48.258 --> 00:02:51.222
And it's because the man didn't have the

00:02:52.081 --> 00:02:53.963
energy, the strength,

00:02:56.411 --> 00:03:00.711
sense of curiosity, of observation,

00:03:01.692 --> 00:03:02.611
of thoughtfulness,

00:03:03.331 --> 00:03:04.792
certainly of responsiveness,

00:03:06.013 --> 00:03:06.992
and of reliability.

00:03:09.173 --> 00:03:12.354
To earn God's trust such that this

00:03:12.454 --> 00:03:16.354
experiment in the enclosed confines of

00:03:16.554 --> 00:03:21.694
Eden could be allowed to grow beyond that,

00:03:22.134 --> 00:03:25.195
such that this one creature

00:03:26.987 --> 00:03:30.430
could be given incremental dimensions,

00:03:31.930 --> 00:03:34.251
be enveloped not in a limiting physical

00:03:34.270 --> 00:03:37.733
