00:05:48.583 --> 00:05:49.343
yeah, that one.

00:05:50.151 --> 00:05:50.932
one has potential,

00:05:50.971 --> 00:05:53.353
that one I think I can work with.

00:05:54.254 --> 00:05:57.276
